Project Setup

This project uses React for the frontend and Node.js for the backend. please Follow the steps below to set up and run the project:

Frontend
Create a React app:

npx create-react-app frontend
Move the frontend files into the src folder:

Ensure all your React components and related files are placed inside the frontend/src folder.
Run the frontend:


cd frontend
npm start


Backend
Create a backend folder:

mkdir backend
cd backend
Initialize the Node.js project:

npm init -y
Add your backend files:

Ensure backend file server.js, are placed inside the backend folder.
Run the backend server:

node server.js
